## Lucide Icons
Use lucide-react for all icons. Import by name and use as components:
```jsx
import { Home, User, Search, Settings, LogOut, Plus, Trash2, Edit, Check, X, ChevronLeft, ChevronRight, Menu, Loader2 } from 'lucide-react';

// Usage - icons accept className and size props
<Home className="w-5 h-5" />
<User size={20} />
<Loader2 className="w-4 h-4 animate-spin" />
```

Common icons: Home, User, Search, Settings, LogOut, LogIn, Plus, Minus, Trash2, Edit, Check, X, ChevronLeft, ChevronRight, ChevronUp, ChevronDown, Menu, MoreHorizontal, MoreVertical, Loader2, RefreshCw, Download, Upload, Copy, Share, Link, AlertTriangle, CheckCircle, XCircle, Info, HelpCircle, Star, Heart, Eye, EyeOff, Lock, Unlock, Filter, ArrowUpDown, Bell, Mail, ShoppingCart, CreditCard, BarChart3, PieChart, TrendingUp

