### 2. Browse / List Page (/browse or domain-appropriate path)
- Search input with visual indicator
- Category/status filter controls
- Sort dropdown
- Items grid or table (use the main list endpoint from the context)
- Pagination controls
- "No results" empty state

### 3. Detail Page (/:resource/:id or domain-appropriate path)
- Full item details (fetched from the detail/single endpoint in the context)
